Eyewitnesses claim two people had an altercation before the shooting took place on Rivonia Road. JOHANNESBURG One person has been shot dead and another wounded in Sandton in the early hours of this morning.Eyewitnesses claim the two had an altercation before the shooting took place on Rivonia Road.ER24 s Werner Vermaak says, One person sustained gun wounds to his chest. He was resuscitated by paramedics but after countless efforts, he was declared dead. Another person sustained gunshot wounds to his head and was rushed to a nearby hospital for further medical care. (Edited by Leeto M Khoza)